---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Default.astro";
import Aside from "../../components/Aside.astro";
import QuoteNow from "../../components/QuoteNow.astro";
const title = "About - Believe Cleaning";
---

<Layout title={title}>
   <section
      class="section is-medium has-background-image"
      data-background="/img/banner-services-int.webp"
      data-position="center 30%"
   >
      <div class="overlay" data-color="#0f466b" data-color-opacity=".35"></div>

      <div class="container">
         <div class="columns is-vcentered is-centered">
            <div class="column is-10 has-text-centered">
               <h1 class="title is-1 is-bold is-spaced light-text">
                  Rental Property Cleaning
               </h1>

               <QuoteNow />
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>

   <!-- About -->

   <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
         <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="columns">
               <div class="column is-8">
                  <div class="content">
                     <figure class="image m-0 mb-5">
                        <img src="/img/services/service-rental-cleaning.webp" alt="" />
                     </figure>

                     <p>
                        Renters try to vacate the rental home in good condition,
                        but this isn’t always possible, or they don’t perform an
                        adequate job. Consider hiring a cleaning service if you
                        want to minimize gaps and get a new renter in as quickly
                        as possible. Believe Cleaning Services in Queens is here
                        to help you with your rental property cleaning needs!
                     </p>

                     <p>
                        Avoid becoming tied to the dirt! Cleaning up a property
                        after someone has moved out of it is an essential part
                        of the process for anyone who owns, manages, or rents
                        the property. Property managers have to be especially
                        critical when tenants clean their apartments because
                        they don’t always realize that cleaning the unit
                        involves more than just vacuuming and wiping down
                        surfaces. For example, they need to ensure that the next
                        occupants won’t find any limescale on the sinks,
                        fingerprints on the switches or other signs of previous
                        occupants’ s poor work.
                     </p>

                     <p>
                        Cleaning a house from top to bottom on your own may be a
                        time-consuming and exhausting task. Think about how much
                        time and effort it will take to fulfill your contract’s
                        requirements to get your full deposit back. Ensure that
                        all necessary materials are purchased, equipment is
                        rented if necessary, and damaged items are replaced or
                        repaired. Clean every inch of the rental property,
                        checking items off your inventory cleaning checklist as
                        you go.
                     </p>

                     <h4 class="title is-4">How Much Is Cleaning Necessary?</h4>

                     <p>
                        The property’s tenants are responsible for cleaning and
                        maintaining the property daily. A lack of hygiene can
                        lead to the development of infections, bug infestations,
                        and mold in the workplace. Removal of these problems is
                        essential. There are times when property management
                        cleaning decides to call in a professional cleaner to do
                        the dirty work for you because of your inadequate
                        performance. Here come our services. Call Believe
                        Cleaning Services, and we’ll make sure everything is
                        spotless while you’re dealing with the stress of
                        relocating! Our rental property cleaning services
                        commonly include a garden, driveway, and patio.
                     </p>

                     <p>
                        Our Rental Property Cleaning typically involves the
                        following:
                     </p>

                     <ul class="normal-list">
                        <li>Kitchen</li>
                        <li>Bathrooms</li>
                        <li>Bedrooms</li>
                        <li>Living rooms</li>
                        <li>Hallway and Stairs</li>
                        <li>Walls</li>
                        <li>Windows</li>
                     </ul>

                     <p>
                        If you want to get your deposit back, you’ll have to
                        spend a lot of time and money cleaning the place, and
                        you’ll also have to buy cleaning products. Instead of
                        wasting your valuable time and resources, hire our
                        cleaning crews to take care of your housekeeping needs.
                     </p>

                     <p>
                        <iframe
                           src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/707335341?h=c656db9f23&title=0&byline=0&portrait=0"
                           width="100%"
                           height="450"
                           frameborder="0"
                           allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
                           allowfullscreen></iframe>
               
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>

               <div class="column is-4">
                  <Aside />
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>
</Layout>
